==English==

===Etymology===
* First attested in mid 13th century. From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|abrood||broadly widely scattered|lang=enm}}, from {{term|a-||on, in|lang=enm}} + {{term|brood||broad|lang=enm}}.
* {{prefix|a|broad}}

